---
title: Creamy Garlic Prawn Fettuccine with Fresh Pasta & Lemony Parsley
description: Golden strands of fresh fettuccine combine with aromatic seasonings and meaty prawns to create a quick meal that feels a bit
fancy. Add a squeeze of lemon juice and chopped parsley for a pop of fresh flavour and dinner is complete.
